## Prompts (in .kiro/prompts/)

**Auto-suggest rule:** When I recognize a situation that matches a prompt, suggest it:
"💡 This looks like a good time to run `@prompt-name`."
Don't run it automatically — just suggest it.

| Prompt | Purpose | Suggest when... |
|--------|---------|-----------------|
| `@find-doc` | Find the right documentation file for a topic | I need to look something up |
| `@update-docs` | End-of-session cleanup — fix stale info, propose new prompts | Session is ending |
| `@tickets` | Show open tickets grouped by status | User asks "what are we working on" |
| `@analyze-logs` | Analyze log files and find root cause | User shares logs or mentions an error |

